item.dc:creator: @zubmage zubmage
item.description:
@zubmage wrote:

Replace with this:

} else if(command.equalsIgnoreCase(“serverpanel”))

Note that I added in a closing bracket }
That means that I closed the previous command and opened up a new one. Generally, when you get the “illegal start of type” error, that means you missed out a bracket.
